en.title: FE Supports Profiles Magazine Launch, Philippines!

table.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(238, 240, 252);

td.strong: REPORT BY PRESIDENTIAL DIRECTOR GRACE KHOO.

tr.td:
FusionExcel International is pleased to sponsor the 11-11-11 Birthday Bash Event held in Penang Time Square on 11th September 2011 from 6pm to 10pm. Lots of people were attracted to know further about FE products and about our company. During the Event, FE product demonstrations and introductions were conducted on the stage.
The Event was attended by more than 1,000 sponsors, children, students, guests, supporters, staffs, newspaper reporters and the public.
FusionExcel was represented by Presidential Director Grace Khoo, Presidential Director Nicole Tan, Presidential Director Billy Ho and Leader Justeen Sim.
Quantum Shields, Premium Quantum Pendants and Quantum Pendants were sponsored by FE and presented to invited VIPs and YB's, organisers, winners, lucky draw winners, the press and media.
Thank you FusionExcel International for the sponsorship and opportunity to promote and share our products and our Social Entrepreneur Program to the public!
AHOO! AHOO!! AHOO!!!
